{"tid":842772,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【回帶】亞視－不思議遊戲","createTime":"2018-09-30T15:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T02:55:29.000Z","uid":193429,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f8ed323fe94e8f03f2dd3030706e7db2132eef5d","tid":842772,"uid":193429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:01:01.000Z","msg":"[size=3]<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/225021_8a6b9577bf293e8f8589f708cda15d13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F225021_8a6b9577bf293e8f8589f708cda15d13.jpg&h=9d0dc621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>《不思議遊戲》</strong><br />\n故事中的國家與角色都是中國風，以四神和二十八星宿為基礎，描述誤入《四神天地書》世界的女主角們分別成為四個不同國家裏代表該國所屬之神的巫女。她們都必須集結自己所屬的七星士，召喚出神明（神獸）拯救國家。其中，女主角夕城美朱被當作是紅南國的「朱雀巫女」，而她也與自己手下「朱雀七星士」之一的鬼宿發展出一段戀愛故事。<br />\n<br />\n亞視播應該係 2001 年嘅事<br />\n果時細細個好鍾意睇依套，最鍾意星宿同翼宿<br />\n但係裡面有啲情節都幾尷尬，唔係幾好意思睇落去<br />\n<br />\n【線上全集】<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av11612042/[/size=4]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav11612042%2F%5B%2Fsize%3D4%5D&d=2j%2F0E%2FhdxIz%2F47vfqW8je0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=dfa8c73f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av11612042/[/size=4]</a>"},{"pid":"07c2a6b3c4d09609ba08f0b5cdf5580b7149b04c","tid":842772,"uid":193429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:01:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">【線上全集】<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av11612042/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav11612042%2F&d=2j%2F0E%2FhdxIz%2F47vfqW8je0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=3275b10f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av11612042/</a></span>"},{"pid":"3a167922a4f04bea2d49b80d9965ead058640a66","tid":842772,"uid":116709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:06:23.000Z","msg":"心宿好型<br />\n<b